  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, I'm Miss Maya. How was your day?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi Maya, my day was okay. I studied for bank exam. Then I watch some football match. Did you see last match of Messi? He was amazing!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it, studying then football, perfect balance. Watching Messi is a treat. What did you love most about his performance?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "His passing was so smart, and he control the ball like it was nothing. I think he is the best player of all time. Do you like football?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said it perfectly, his control is like magic. Football is fun to watch. Do you play it too?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, I play football sometimes with my friends. We play in a small ground near my home. Not as good as Messi, of course! Ha ha. But it's fun. Do you like any sport?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You play with friends, that's the best way to enjoy. I like watching cricket, but I don't play much. What's your favourite part of playing football?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The best part is when you score a goal and your friends cheer for you. It makes me feel happy and proud. Also, when we win the match, we celebrate like champions! Sometimes we even take photo. Do you watch cricket a lot?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Scoring and hearing cheers is the best, you sound like a natural. Taking photos after wins is a great way to remember the fun. I watch cricket matches often. What’s your take on cricket?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I know little about cricket, but I think it's a good game. I watch it sometimes when my friends are watching. The batting and bowling is interesting. Do you like any particular team?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said it right, batting and bowling are the stars. I support no team, but I love how cricket brings people together. What's your take on the game's slow pace?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The slow pace can be a bit boring for me, but I guess that’s what makes it a thinking game. In football, it’s fast and action all the time. But in cricket, you need patience, like waiting for a long over. My friends and I sometimes argue about which game is better! What do you think?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re doing great, that’s a thoughtful way to put it. Cricket asks you to wait and think, football makes you move and react. Both are fun in their way. What’s your team’s stance, football or cricket?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "In football, we just enjoy the game without taking sides, but in cricket, my friends are very passionate about their teams. I don’t really support any team, but I like watching the action. Maybe one day I’ll try to understand it better. Okay, I should get back to studying now. Talk to you soon!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're doing great, and that's the best way to enjoy any sport, just watching the action. Studying calls, then. Keep up the good work! Tell me how your match goes next time."
    }
  ],
